---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Family Offices — Crypto Allocation Guide">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Family Offices</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">HK Family Office<br/>Crypto Allocation Guide</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">香港家族辦公室<br/>加密資產配置指南</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">52% of Hong Kong family offices plan to allocate to crypto. Digital assets now qualify for the same profit tax exemptions as equities and bonds. Here's what you need to know.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">52%的香港家族辦公室計劃配置加密資產。數字資產現已享有與股票及債券相同的利得稅豁免。以下是你需要了解的內容。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">3,380+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Family offices in HK</span><span class="lang-zh">香港家族辦公室</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">52%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Plan crypto allocation</span><span class="lang-zh">計劃配置加密資產</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">27%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Within 6 months</span><span class="lang-zh">6個月內行動</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-400">Feb 2026</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Tax concession effective</span><span class="lang-zh">稅務優惠生效</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tax Concession -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">The Tax Concession: What Changed</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">稅務優惠：變化了什���</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-cyan-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">Before (Pre-Feb 2026)</span><span class="lang-zh">之前（2026年2月前）</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="lang-en">Digital assets were <span class="text-white font-medium">not listed</span> as qualifying investments under the family office tax concession regime.</span><span class="lang-zh">數字資產<span class="text-white font-medium">未被列入</span>家族辦公室稅務優惠制度的合資格投資範圍。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en">Family offices had to independently evaluate the tax treatment of crypto investments — high legal costs, significant uncertainty.</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室需自行評估加密投資的稅務處理 — 法律成本高、不確定性大。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en">This ambiguity was a major barrier to institutional crypto allocation in HK.</span><span class="lang-zh">這種模糊性是香港機構加密資產配置的主要障礙。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
            <span class="lang-en">After (Feb 2026 Onwards)</span><span class="lang-zh">之後（2026年2月起）</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
            <p><span class="lang-en">Digital assets are <span class="text-white font-medium">officially listed</span> as qualifying investments.</span><span class="lang-zh">數字資產<span class="text-white font-medium">正式列入</span>合資格投資範圍。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Profit tax exemption</span> applies to digital asset investments, same treatment as equities, bonds, and other qualifying assets.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">利得稅豁免</span>適用於數字資產投資，與股票、債券及其他合資格資產享受相同待��。</span></p>
            <p><span class="lang-en">Tax treatment is now <span class="text-white font-medium">consistent with traditional assets</span> — removing the legal uncertainty that previously blocked allocation.</span><span class="lang-zh">稅務處理現已<span class="text-white font-medium">與傳統資產一致</span> — 消除了此前阻礙配置的法律不確定性。</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Allocation Framework -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Allocation Framework</span><span class="lang-zh">配置框��</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">1</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
            <span class="lang-en">Conservative: Tokenized Treasuries Only</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">保守：僅代幣化美債</span>
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 space-y-2">
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Products:</span> BlackRock BUIDL ($2.9B AUM), Franklin Templeton BENJI ($742M AUM).</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">產品：</span>BlackRock BUIDL ($2.9B AUM)、Franklin Templeton BENJI ($742M AUM)。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Risk:</span> US Treasury credit risk + smart contract risk. Same underlying as a traditional money market fund.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">風險：</span>美國國債信用風險 + 智能合約風險。底層資產與傳統貨幣市場基金相同。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Suitable for:</span> First-time crypto allocation. Meets fiduciary standard — BlackRock and Franklin Templeton are familiar names.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">適合：</span>首次加密資產配置。符合受託標準 — BlackRock和Franklin Templeton是熟悉的品牌���</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">2</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
            <span class="lang-en">Moderate: Core Holdings + Staking Yield</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">穩健：核心持倉 + 質押收益</span>
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 space-y-2">
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Products:</span> BTC + ETH via licensed VATPs (HashKey, OSL). ETH staking for ~3-4% APR.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">產品：</span>通過持牌VATP（HashKey、OSL）購買BTC + ETH。ETH質押約3-4% APR。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Risk:</span> Crypto market volatility. SFC-regulated custody and staking mitigates operational risk.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">風險：</span>加密市場波動。SFC監管的託管和質押緩解運營風險。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Suitable for:</span> Family offices with existing alternative asset allocation. SFC staking approval (April 2025) makes this a regulated yield product.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">適合：</span>已有另類資產配置的家族辦公室。SFC質押批准（2025年4月）使其成為受監管的收益產品。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">3</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
            <span class="lang-en">Growth: DeFi Yield + Onchain Strategies</span>
            <span class="lang-zh">增長：DeFi收益 + 鏈上策略</span>
          </h3>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 space-y-2">
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Strategies:</span> Stablecoin lending (3-8% APR), LP on AMMs, pre-IPO perps via Hyperliquid.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">策略：</span>穩定幣借貸（3-8% APR）、AMM流動性提供、通過Hyperliquid交易Pre-IPO永續合約。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Risk:</span> Smart contract risk, impermanent loss, counterparty risk. Not regulated by SFC.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">風險：</span>智能合約風險、無常損失、對手方風險。不受SFC監管。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Suitable for:</span> Offices with crypto-experienced staff or dedicated digital asset mandate.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">適合：</span>擁有加密經驗人員或專門數字資產授權的辦公室。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Operational Considerations -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Operational Considerations</span><span class="lang-zh">運營考量</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Custody</span><span class="lang-zh">託管</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Licensed VATPs (HashKey, OSL) provide SFC-regulated custody. For larger allocations, dedicated institutional custodians (e.g., Hex Trust, Anchorage Digital) offer insurance-backed cold storage. Upcoming VA custodian licensing (2026) will expand options.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">持牌VATP（HashKey、OSL）提供SFC監管的託管。對於較大配置，專門的機構託管人（如Hex Trust、Anchorage Digital）提供有保險的冷存儲。即將推出的VA託管人牌照（2026年）將擴大選擇。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Compliance & Reporting</span><span class="lang-zh">合規與報告</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Onchain assets provide verifiable audit trails. NAV tracking is real-time. Work with your tax advisor to ensure digital asset investments qualify under the family office tax concession regime — the Feb 2026 amendment provides clear guidance, but specific structuring may vary.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">鏈上資產提供可驗證的審計軌跡。資產淨值跟蹤實時進行。與你的稅務顧問合作，確保數字資產投資符合家族辦公室稅務優惠制度的資格 — 2026年2月修訂提供明確指引，但具體結構可能有所不同。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Evaluating crypto allocation for your family office?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">為你的家族辦公室評估加密資產配置？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We provide guidance on products, custody, and tax structuring for HK family offices.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們為香港家族辦公室提供產品、託管及稅務結構方面的指導。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-between">
      <a href={`${base}/apply/asset-management`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">← Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">← 資產管理</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/apply/prop-trading`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">Prop Trading →</span><span class="lang-zh">自營交易 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
